<title>BRAZIL: Brazil markets closed for Easter.</title>
<headline>Brazil markets closed for Easter.</headline>
<dateline>BRASILIA 1997-03-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Brazilian financial markets are closed Thursday and Friday for the Easter holiday.</p>
<p>Markets reopen Monday as normal.</p>
<p>((-- Michael Christie, Brasilia newsroom 55-61-2230358))</p>
